episodes.synopsis: When smugglers arrive from Guyana, customs officers have to employ special skills to find cocaine concealed in some very out-of-the-way places.
episodes.title: Cavity Courier

episodes.synopsis: Special agents examine a package containing engine pistons that vary in weight, propelling them to drill for drugs and zero in on a heroin trafficker.
episodes.title: Hidden Heroin

episodes.synopsis: Agents find a bunch of leather coats with cocaine hidden inside their linings; radiation warnings spread alarm among passengers.
episodes.title: Coke in the Coat

episodes.synopsis: Agents see cocaine leaking out of the cracks in a teenager's luggage and nab the youngster, urging him to begin naming names.
episodes.title: Search & Seize

episodes.synopsis: A courier detained for carrying four kilos of cocaine stonewalls authorities, refusing to give the name of the intended recipient.
episodes.title: Courier to Kingpin

video.title: To Catch a Smuggler
video.synopsis: Homeland Security officers at New York's JFK International Airport deal with drug smuggling, human trafficking and more in this documentary series.
